Definition: a strong belief in a supernatural power or powers that control human destiny
Example: he lost his faith but not his morality
Synonyms: adj, all, religious, noun, person, religionist, faith, religious_belief, belief, attribute, theological_virtue, a, strong, in, supernatural, power, or, powers, that, control, human, destiny, he, lost, his, but, not, morality
Category: noun.cognition
